description:
This is a 5 minute workout called '5 Minute Mindfulness Meditation' from the channel Great Meditation.
The workout falls under Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Deep Recharge vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Here you can listen to one of our original 5 minute guided mindfulness meditations, recorded by us...  for you to use when you are short on time, but still want to get into a mindful state of mind.  Even five minutes can produce major benefits, give it a try... Enjoy!

Spoken Voice: Original Commentary recorded by us.
